org.workflowsim

Class Job

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudbus.cloudsim.Cloudlet
      • org.workflowsim.Task
        • org.workflowsim.Job

  • public class Job
extends Task
    Job is an extention to Task. It is basically a group of tasks. In WorkflowSim, the ClusteringEngine merges tasks into jobs (group of tasks) and the overall runtime of a job is the sum of the task runtime.
    Since:
    WorkflowSim Toolkit 1.0
